Most U.K. shares rose as the FTSE 100
Index advanced 0.1 percent to 5,850.01 at 8:34 a.m. in  London .  Standard Chartered Plc, Glencore International Plc and
Randgold Resources Ltd. paced advances as Amec Plc and BT Group
Plc lead decliners.  To contact the reporter on this story:
